Articles.Content: Hi do you have plugins running any part of that craft?  I've seen similar things happen when a part module is destroyed and the code fails to catch the exceptions,  Check the KSP.log,

This is a modeed Pod i created with an existing IVA from Inline Cockpit. No plugin added simply a model with an modded .cfg.

Sincerly i have no idea why that bug happen.

Edited May 9, 2017 by Warsoul

Was there anything in the log?  I'm half expecting there to be a, look rotation vector = zero, error,  which could, perhaps,  indicate a problem with the gear, I gather from your (mod)parts list that you've made your own gear,  is it separate from the ship or built in? (edit ignore that i 've just watched video again and see craft is 9 parts, so gear is presumably surface attach)

( ps if you're interested,  I'd be happy to get your point defense turret BDA ready)

Edited May 9, 2017 by SpannerMonkey(smce)
re watched video
